        "content": "函数后面-&gt;是什么鬼？我怎么从来没见过？是无敌的正则表达式吗？决定函数类型？",
        "likes": 1,
        "unlikes": 0,
        "replies": 4,
        "top": 0,
        "removed": 0,
        "links": null,
        "created_at": "2022-07-12 20:44:50",
        "comment_from": "topic",
        "username": "小轩",
        "user_avatar_path": "https://static1.xesimg.com/udc-o-user-avatar/20240907/TalzonWMSyKikgD5ZEDafJ9YyA_d75edba0b573c72c.png",
